<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 22:06:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>俄罗斯准备与外国人签署“忠诚协议”以阻止政策批评</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-preparing-a-loyalty-agreement-for-foreigners-to-stop-policy-criticism/articleshow/105602973.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105602973.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 21:07:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-preparing-a-loyalty-agreement-for-foreigners-to-stop-policy-criticism/articleshow/105602973.cms</guid></item><item><title>官方：美国12月起开始更新国内工作签证</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/official-us-to-begin-domestic-work-visa-renewal-from-december/articleshow/105602934.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105602934.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国正在启动某些类别H-1B签证在国内续签的试点计划，使大批印度科技专业人士受益。该倡议最初仅限于 20,000 名参与者，旨在满足高需求并减少等待时间，重点关注印度。负责签证服务的副助理国务卿朱莉·斯塔夫特（Julie Stufft）强调，该计划旨在为已经在该国的外国人提供签证续签，从而无需返回本国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 20:57:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/official-us-to-begin-domestic-work-visa-renewal-from-december/articleshow/105602934.cms</guid></item><item><title>“气候变化会议是一个机会——如果我们都发挥自己的作用”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/climate-change-conference-is-an-opportunity-if-we-all-play-our-part/articleshow/105602936.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105602936.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 20:57:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/climate-change-conference-is-an-opportunity-if-we-all-play-our-part/articleshow/105602936.cms</guid></item><item><title>里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 因帕台农神庙雕塑引发与希腊的争执</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/rishi-sunak-fuels-row-with-greece-over-parthenon-sculptures/articleshow/105602898.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105602898.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国首相里希·苏纳克指责希腊总理基里亚科斯·米佐塔基斯在访问伦敦期间对帕台农神庙雕塑“哗众取宠”，导致计划中的会议被取消。苏纳克声称米佐塔基斯违背了不主张归还埃尔金大理石浮雕的承诺。希腊政府的回应是强调需要维持长期关系。米佐塔基斯后来缓和了言辞，称会议的取消是“不幸的事件”。这场争端加剧了文物所有权问题上的紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 20:47:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/rishi-sunak-fuels-row-with-greece-over-parthenon-sculptures/articleshow/105602898.cms</guid></item><item><title>尼泊尔第一桩同性婚姻登记</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/first-same-sex-marriage-is-registered-in-nepal/articleshow/105602899.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105602899.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 20:47:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/first-same-sex-marriage-is-registered-in-nepal/articleshow/105602899.cms</guid></item><item><title>亲戚们说，当孩子们哭泣时，哈马斯绑架者就会用枪威胁他们</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/when-children-cried-they-were-threatened-with-gun-by-hamas-captors-say-relatives/articleshow/105602789.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105602789.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 12 岁的埃坦·亚哈洛米 (Eitan Yahalomi) 和 9 岁的艾米丽·汉德 (Emily Hand) 在加沙被哈马斯扣为人质 50 多天。据称，埃坦遭到殴打，并被迫观看哈马斯袭击的视频，而艾米丽回家后默默哭泣，并习惯于不发出声音。人质的遭遇仍部分未知，其中一些人可能需要治疗，强调需要恢复控制感并为他们的康复提供支持。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 20:11:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/when-children-cried-they-were-threatened-with-gun-by-hamas-captors-say-relatives/articleshow/105602789.cms</guid></item><item><title>前人质称在隧道中与哈马斯加沙酋长对质</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/ex-hostage-says-confronted-hamas-gaza-chief-in-tunnel/articleshow/105602791.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105602791.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 20:11:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/ex-hostage-says-confronted-hamas-gaza-chief-in-tunnel/articleshow/105602791.cms</guid></item><item><title>报道称，加拿大与谷歌达成协议，将在搜索结果中保留新闻</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/canada-google-reach-deal-to-keep-news-in-search-results-says-report/articleshow/105602792.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105602792.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据报道，加拿大和谷歌就一项新法律的争议达成协议，该法律要求大型互联网公司与新闻出版商分享广告收入。如果得到确认，该交易将阻止谷歌屏蔽其平台上的新闻。据报道，该协议涉及谷歌每年向新闻公司支付约 1 亿加元（7360 万美元），以换取继续在其平台上分享加拿大新闻。作为全球趋势的一部分，《在线新闻法案》于 6 月获得通过，政府预计将于 12 月 19 日敲定规则。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 20:11:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/canada-google-reach-deal-to-keep-news-in-search-results-says-report/articleshow/105602792.cms</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔举行会谈以延长停火协议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/talks-on-in-qatar-to-extend-truce/articleshow/105602713.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105602713.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列和哈马斯在加沙的停火将在交换人质和囚犯后结束。希望这些短期停火最终将导致就长期停火进行谈判。然而，达成全面协议仍然具有挑战性，以色列的目标是消灭哈马斯及其在加沙的基础设施。目前的停火依赖于人质和囚犯的交换，这一过程可能会变得更加复杂，因为谈判涉及被俘的战斗人员，其中包括以色列关押的备受瞩目的巴勒斯坦囚犯。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 19:53:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/talks-on-in-qatar-to-extend-truce/articleshow/105602713.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊姆兰辞去 PTI 主席职务，任命助手戈哈尔·汗为“临时”继任者</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/imran-steps-down-as-pti-chief-picks-aide-gohar-khan-as-interim-successor/articleshow/105602384.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105602384.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊姆兰·汗 (Imran Khan) 辞去巴基斯坦正义运动 (PTI) 领导人职务，在面临法律挑战的情况下，临时安排将权力移交给亲密伙伴戈哈尔·阿里·汗 (Gohar Ali Khan)。伊姆兰是在托沙卡纳贪污案被定罪后做出这一决定的。此举旨在防止选举监督机构干扰并维护政党的诚信。伊姆兰计划在迅速解决法律问题后参加党内民意调查。戈哈尔对被选为巴基斯坦主要反对党领袖表示感谢。 “我很震惊。无法用语言来表达我对伊姆兰·汗先生的感激之情。”</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 19:03:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/imran-steps-down-as-pti-chief-picks-aide-gohar-khan-as-interim-successor/articleshow/105602384.cms</guid></item><item><title>尼泊尔登记第一例正式同性婚姻</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nepal-registers-first-official-same-sex-marriage/articleshow/105602685.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105602685.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;尼泊尔最高法院将同性婚姻合法化五个月后，周三正式登记了第一起同性婚姻案件。尼泊尔成为第一个办理结婚登记的南亚国家。致力于尼泊尔性少数群体权利和福利的组织蓝钻协会主席 Sanjib Gurung (Pinky) 表示，这次结合在尼泊尔西部 Lamjung 区的 Dordi 农村市举行了隆重仪式并正式登记。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 19:46:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nepal-registers-first-official-same-sex-marriage/articleshow/105602685.cms</guid></item><item><title>法院宣判纳瓦兹·谢里夫在与巴拿马文件有关的贪污案中无罪</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/court-acquits-nawaz-sharif-in-graft-case-linked-to-panama-papers/articleshow/105602392.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105602392.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周三，伊斯兰堡高等法院宣布巴基斯坦前总理纳瓦兹·谢里夫在与购买伦敦四套豪华公寓有关的阿文菲尔德腐败案中无罪，推翻了问责法庭对他判处的 10 年监禁。谢里夫被首席大法官阿梅尔·法鲁克领导的两名法官无罪释放，此前他的女儿玛丽亚姆·纳瓦兹和女婿萨夫达尔·阿万在同一案件中被无罪释放。阿文菲尔德案是与 2016 年巴拿马文件丑闻相关的三起案件之一。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 18:52:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/court-acquits-nawaz-sharif-in-graft-case-linked-to-panama-papers/articleshow/105602392.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列和哈马斯同意将休战期再延长两天，并释放更多人质和囚犯</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-and-hamas-agree-to-extend-truce-for-two-more-days-and-to-free-more-hostages-and-prisoners/articleshow/105601977.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105601977.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列和哈马斯同意将停火期限再延长两天，这增加了进一步用武装分子扣押的人质交换被以色列囚禁的巴勒斯坦人的可能性，并延长了他们最致命和最具破坏性的战争的停顿时间。哈马斯释放的 11 名以色列妇女和儿童周一晚上进入以色列，此前他们在加沙被囚禁了七周多，这是原定为期四天的休战协议下的第四次交换，休战协议于周五开始，预计将结束。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 18:04:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-and-hamas-agree-to-extend-truce-for-two-more-days-and-to-free-more-hostages-and-prisoners/articleshow/105601977.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国制裁与伊朗石油销售有关的金融网络</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-sanctions-financial-network-tied-to-iranian-oil-sales/articleshow/105601806.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105601806.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国周三表示，对涉嫌参与为伊朗军方谋取利益的金融便利网络的 20 名个人和公司实施新一轮制裁。财政部的制裁影响了从香港到阿拉伯联合酋长国的公司和个人。制裁阻止进入美国财产和银行账户，并阻止目标个人和公司与美国人做生意。白宫表示，尚未发现伊朗直接参与 10 月 7 日针对以色列的多管齐下行动的信息。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 17:40:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-sanctions-financial-network-tied-to-iranian-oil-sales/articleshow/105601806.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方表示正在调查哈马斯关于婴儿人质死亡的报告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-army-says-investigating-hamas-report-of-baby-hostage-death/articleshow/105601730.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105601730.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列军队周三表示，正在调查哈马斯武装派别的一份报告，称一名 10 个月大的婴儿人质、他四岁的兄弟和他们的母亲均在加沙被杀。军方此前声称，60 名人质在以色列爆炸事件中丧生。该数字尚未得到验证。以色列南部尼尔奥兹基布兹婴儿被绑架的画面已成为这起致命袭击事件的象征之一。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 17:33:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-army-says-investigating-hamas-report-of-baby-hostage-death/articleshow/105601730.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯寡头普普杨斯基之子赢得针对欧盟制裁的上诉</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/son-of-russian-oligarch-pumpyansky-wins-appeal-against-eu-sanctions/articleshow/105601639.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105601639.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;欧盟法院周三表示，俄罗斯大亨德米特里·庞普扬斯基 (Dmitry Pumpyansky) 之子亚历山大·庞普扬斯基 (Alexander Pumpyansky) 在针对欧盟因俄罗斯入侵乌克兰而实施的制裁的上诉中获胜。法院在裁决中表示，欧盟理事会承认，自 2022 年 3 月 9 日起，即入侵乌克兰两周后、第一轮制裁前六个月，Pumpyansky 不再担任 Sinara 董事会主席和成员，也不再担任董事会成员。 TMK 成员，这也是将他列入制裁名单的原因。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 17:23:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/son-of-russian-oligarch-pumpyansky-wins-appeal-against-eu-sanctions/articleshow/105601639.cms</guid></item><item><title>帝国公民：随着德国组织的壮大，袭击和怀疑</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/citizens-of-the-reich-raids-and-suspicion-as-german-group-grows/articleshow/105594461.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105594461.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;自称国王的彼得·菲茨克领导的“德意志王国”挑战现代德国的合法性，形成了帝国布尔格运动。该组织拥有超过 5,000 名追随者，建立自己的法律、货币和卫生系统，倡导不吸烟、不饮酒和反疫苗接种的信念。当局突击搜查了涉嫌非法金融活动的网站。该运动的人数不断增加，并面临针对国家的暴力阴谋的指控。虽然他们大多来自社会弱势群体，但人们担心他们与右翼分子的潜在联系。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 11:13:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/citizens-of-the-reich-raids-and-suspicion-as-german-group-grows/articleshow/105594461.cms</guid></item><item><title>欧盟减少工业排放协议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/eu-agreement-on-reducing-industrial-emissions/articleshow/105593692.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105593692.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;欧盟成员国和欧洲议会周三表示，他们已就遏制工业排放达成初步协议，其中包括集约化家禽养殖场、养猪场以及矿场的工业排放。代表成员国的欧洲理事会在一份声明中表示，该协议于周二晚间达成，将“减少工业有害排放并改善公众获取信息的机会”。该文件的主要欧盟议员拉丹·卡内夫表示，这将“显着”减少排放。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 10:46:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/eu-agreement-on-reducing-industrial-emissions/articleshow/105593692.cms</guid></item><item><title>孟加拉国反对派誓言尽管遭到“专制”镇压仍将继续抗议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/bangladesh-opposition-vows-to-continue-protests-despite-autocratic-crackdown/articleshow/105593329.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105593329.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 10:36:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/bangladesh-opposition-vows-to-continue-protests-despite-autocratic-crackdown/articleshow/105593329.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦前总理谢巴兹·谢里夫：5月9日的暴力事件是为了推翻陆军参谋长阿西姆·穆尼尔将军</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/may-9-violence-was-an-attempt-to-topple-army-chief-gen-asim-munir-ex-pakistan-pm-shehbaz-sharif/articleshow/105592412.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/105592412.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 10:13:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/may-9-violence-was-an-attempt-to-topple-army-chief-gen-asim-munir-ex-pakistan-pm-shehbaz-sharif/articleshow/105592412.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>